OL,3,CWork-from-home surgeons 'hard to
OL,4,Cprocess,' says health minister
OL,6,FThe Health Minister has described the
OL,7,Fculture at Northern Ireland's Cardiac
OL,8,FSurgery Unit as "appalling" after UTV
OL,9,Frevealed findings of a report which
OL,10,Fsaid that the "poor behaviour" of some
OL,11,Fsenior medics had led to a
OL,12,F"significant risk to patient safety."
OL,14,FThis follows the cancellation of
OL,15,Foperations earlier this year, after
OL,16,Ffour heart surgeons refused to attend
OL,17,Ftheatre following a breakdown in
OL,18,Fworking relations between some staff
OL,19,Fmembers.
