OL,6,FIn Belfast, almost 1000 operations are
OL,7,Fcarried out by the Trust's Cardiac
OL,8,FSurgery Unit every year.
OL,10,FThe inspection report, seen by UTV
OL,11,Flast week, highlights a "pattern of
OL,12,Fconsistently poor behaviour on the
OL,13,Fpart of a minority of senior
OL,14,Fconsultants" at the facility in the
OL,15,FRoyal Victoria hospital.
OL,17,FShockingly, in their report,
OL,18,Finspectors said: "The cultural issues
OL,19,Fin this unit represent a significant
OL,20,Frisk to patient safety."
