OL,3,CWork-from-home surgeons 'hard to
OL,4,Cprocess,' says health minister
OL,6,FLast week in a statement the Trust
OL,7,Fsaid: "Belfast Trust is appalled by
OL,8,Fthe staff experiences described in an
OL,9,Findependent external review into the
OL,10,Fculture and safety within the cardiac
OL,11,Fsurgical unit at the Royal Victoria
OL,12,FHospital. While we are reassured that
OL,13,Fthe cardiac surgery service remains
OL,14,Fclinically safe with excellent
OL,15,Foutcomes, we accept that there have
OL,16,Fbeen behaviours which, at times, have
OL,17,Fmade for an intolerable working
OL,18,Fenvironment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
